short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collect addresses and build Google Maps link

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Mr. Timo with Goggles is a tool designed to help you collect addresses from Timo marketplace and automatically generate Google Maps links for easy navigation. The extension grab all loading and unloading places and automaticly generates google maps link. 

The free version offers a limited number of clicks per day, while the premium version unlocks unlimited clicks. It's perfect for professionals who frequently need to calculate routes or manage multiple destinations. Upgrade to the premium version to remove the click limit and enjoy seamless navigation assistance.
